I20030211

Following is the code to create a figure for an EditPart.
When such a figure was added to the canvas a stack overflow occured.
Removing the setConstrant fixed the problem.

protected IFigure createFigure() {
	Label label = new Label();
	label.setBorder(new LineBorder());
	BorderLayout borderLayout = new BorderLayout();
	label.setLayoutManager(borderLayout);
	borderLayout.setConstraint(label, BorderLayout.CENTER);
	return label;
}

